title: Female Metal Power Volume 1
description:
Like most of you I got tired of listening to half way decent to complete crappy Female Metal collections.Sorry but alot of it has poor production or the girl can't sing to save her life.
So having said that I decided to go through...yet again my personal metal collection and i created 3 volumes around 700mb each out of about 60gb of Female Fronted Metal.
These three volumes have nothing but kickass stuff on them.No b-sides or poor production or the like.
Just great frigging metal with a cool Luis Royo painting as an album cover stuck to it.
Quality on all tracks is 320kbps and all are properly tagged..at least in Mediamonkey because thats all i use.
So enjoy and SEED and happy listening to this first of three!

PapaPitufo
